main event: A witness observed a bright silvery object that had a flight pattern different than a jet aircraft. The observation lasted for 10 minutes.
interesting points: The object had various descriptions in the available data, such as size, shape, color, and motion.
The object flew away and disappeared.
The object moved behind and in front of clouds at times.
The object was estimated to be small in size and dark in color.
The object moved more rapidly than a jet aircraft and made square, definite turns unlike smooth aircraft movements.
